{
  "stem": "24268.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So the old-- the older woman, she-- I went-- while I was waiting for the-- the connection-- was talking to her.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I spoke German too.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she said, just too bad, she said to my husband.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't have my husband.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I would love to have you, adopt.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I said, what the irony of my life.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I say if they knew what-- who I am-- [LAUGHS] that I am Jewish, she had tried to destroy us.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they want to adopt you-- how the irony of life can be.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Anyway--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I left-- excuse me?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had to go back there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There's no other way.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't want to stay in Sosnowiec.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From Peterswaldau I went-- I was with this cousins.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I guess it was the two ladies.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One I didn't know, then was a cousin of my husband.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, not then.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And also with the other lady-- but then I went back again to Sosnowiec, because she ask me-- the cousin-- to go back to home to help the cousin, whatever.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I couldn't refuse the brother or sister.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she-- she-- they found each other, the sister-- the younger sister.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then while I was walking the street-- that was [NON-ENGLISH] in Sosnowiec-- with her-- she noticed a young man walking, and this was my husband.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She said, you know, if you excuse me, I think I-- this young man must be a relative.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so I said, OK.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so she approached him, and she asked him and said, I think they come.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The name was [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Now one of the [NON-ENGLISH], they were very well to do-- the cousins I knew.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I-- I didn't really know, but my cousin knew.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
